OL,3,CNI Secretary declines to put figure on
OL,4,CCasement funding
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,7,Fhas declined to put a figure on how
OL,8,Fmuch the UK Government is willing to
OL,9,Fcontribute to the redevelopment of
OL,10,FCasement Park.
OL,12,FIt comes after the government
OL,13,Fannounced it will not fund the west
OL,14,FBelfast stadium in time for the Euros
OL,15,Fin 2028, due to "a significant risk
OL,16,Fthat it would not be built in time".
OL,18,FThe secretary of state said the
OL,19,Fdecision had been taken with "deep
OL,20,Fregret".
