OL,6,F"After the news that it is just not
OL,7,Fpossible to build Casement Park for
OL,8,Fthe Euros because however much money
OL,9,Fwe were prepared to put into it there
OL,10,Fwas a real risk the stadium would not
OL,11,Fbe complete on time, I think everyone
OL,12,Fneeds to take stock," Hilary Benn told
OL,13,FUTV.
