OL,3,CNI Secretary declines to put figure on
OL,4,CCasement funding
OL,6,F"I will be talking with all of the
OL,7,Fpartners in the next few days to work
OL,8,Fout where we go from here given that
OL,9,Fthe Euros is unfortunately - and it is
OL,10,Fa decision we took with deep regret -
OL,11,Fnot possible but frankly in the 18
OL,12,Fmonths previously nothing had been
OL,13,Fdone to advance the project which is
OL,14,Fwhy we were left with an impossible
OL,15,Fsituation."
OL,17,FHe refused to state how much the
OL,18,Fgovernment would add.
