OL,3,CNI Secretary declines to put figure on
OL,4,CCasement funding
OL,6,F"We are just going to have to take
OL,7,Fstock, we know how much is in the pot,
OL,8,Fthe design is going to have to be
OL,9,Frethought, so there are lots of
OL,10,Fquestions we can't answer at the
OL,11,Fmoment, but I'm determined to work
OL,12,Fwith other partners to work out how we
OL,13,Fcan take this project forward and
OL,14,Fhonour the long-standing commitment of
OL,15,Fthe Northern Ireland Executive that
OL,16,FCasement Park will be built."
OL,18,FHe explained the #400million figure
OL,19,Ffor the project build was in the
OL,20,Fmiddle of an estimate they have
OL,21,Fobtained from experts.
