OL,6,FEarlier, Taoiseach Simon Harris said
OL,7,Fthe Irish Government "is open" to have
OL,8,Fconversations about more that can be
OL,9,Fdone to help in relation to Casement
OL,10,FPark.
OL,12,FHe has said his government remained
OL,13,Fcommitted to the 50 million euro (#42
OL,14,Fmillion) pledge to rebuild the sports
OL,15,Fground.
OL,17,FWhen asked whether he was ruling out
OL,18,Fpledging further funding during a
OL,19,Fvisit to Londonderry on Monday, Mr
OL,20,FHarris said he was not ruling it out
OL,21,For in.
