OL,6,F"The Irish Government is open to
OL,7,Fcontinuing to have conversations about
OL,8,Fanything more we can do to help, but
OL,9,Fwe're not quite there yet," the
OL,10,FTaoiseach said.
OL,12,F"What we now need to see is what the
OL,13,FBritish Government and the Northern
OL,14,FIreland Executive wanted to do next.
OL,16,F"We stand ready to assist in any
OL,17,Fpractical way that we can."
